<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ [سورة الغاشية <span class="c2">(٨٨)</span>: آية ١]<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>هَلْ أَتاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغاشِيَةِ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
