<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ خاشِعَةٌ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> عامِلَةٌ ناصِبَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> تَصْلى ناراً حامِيَةً <span class="c2">(٤)</span> تُسْقى مِنْ عَيْنٍ آنِيَةٍ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> لَيْسَ لَهُمْ طَعامٌ إِلاَّ مِنْ ضَرِيعٍ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>لا يُسْمِنُ وَلا يُغْنِي مِنْ جُوعٍ <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>